SUMMARY:Healing Arts One-Time Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Pence Adult Art Programs\nPart of the Pence's Healing Arts Pro
 gram and run by facilitator Amy Vidra\, this one-time workshop focuses mor
 e broadly on themes related to depression\, anxiety\, or major life change
 s. Through the process of art making\, participants will have opportunitie
 s for discussion\, education\, and connecting with peers in a safe and sup
 portive space.\n\nREGISTRATION ONLINE IS REQUIRED IN ADVANCE through the P
 ence Gallery's website\, and space is limited to the first 8 participants 
 who register. Participants must be 18 or older\, and no art experience is 
 necessary. This program is generously sponsored by Bob & Joanne Andresen.\
 n\nHealing Arts One-Time Workshop\nMonday\, May 18\, 10-11:45 AM\n$5 Membe
 rs\, $10 Non-Members (all materials included)\n\n**Reminder - an RSVP on M
 eetup does NOT count as registration. Registration is required in advance 
 through the [Pence’s website (CLICK HERE)](https://pencegallery.org/educ
 ation/programs/workshops-and-classes/).**\n\n\\*If you register for this s
 ession and are unable to attend\, please let us know in advance.\n\nAny qu
 estions? Email pencegallery@gmail.com.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/pence-adult-art-programs/events/31415
 5530/
